You were really bad.

00:07:54.162 --> 00:07:56.620
If you had to be stuck in an
elevator with either President

00:07:56.620 --> 00:07:59.564
Trump, Mike Pence, or Jeff
Sessions, who would it be?

00:07:59.564 --> 00:08:01.260
[LAUGHTER]

00:08:01.260 --> 00:08:04.092
Does one of us have
to come out alive?

00:08:04.092 --> 00:08:06.978
[LAUGHTER]

00:08:06.978 --> 00:08:10.345
[APPLAUSE]

