You can't sleep in
the middle of night.

00:08:14.860 --> 00:08:16.780
What do you do?

00:08:16.780 --> 00:08:20.060
Oh, I get up.

00:08:20.060 --> 00:08:22.060
I will read cookbooks.

00:08:22.060 --> 00:08:24.100
I actually-- this
happened recently.

00:08:24.100 --> 00:08:24.880
Yeah.

00:08:24.880 --> 00:08:25.870
I love cooking.

00:08:25.870 --> 00:08:27.220
You just read cookbooks?

00:08:27.220 --> 00:08:28.360
I read recipes.

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:31.756
I'd like recipes
if I'm not cooking.

00:08:31.756 --> 00:08:33.130
Especially if
you're not cooking.

00:08:33.130 --> 00:08:33.760
Yeah.

00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:34.840
[LAUGHTER]

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:37.850
What's a nickname that
your husband calls you?

00:08:37.850 --> 00:08:39.679
Honey, babe.

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:40.260
The regular?

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:41.929
Yeah.

00:08:41.929 --> 00:08:45.350
What's a nickname your
Republican colleagues call you?

00:08:45.350 --> 00:08:46.892
I have no idea.

00:08:46.892 --> 00:08:48.218
[LAUGHTER]

00:08:48.218 --> 00:08:50.170
All right.

00:08:50.170 --> 00:08:51.830
Let's see.

