No.

00:08:53.690 --> 00:08:55.490
If you were going to get a
tattoo, what would it be?

00:08:55.490 --> 00:08:56.406
And where would it go?

00:08:58.940 --> 00:09:01.504
If I were to get
a tattoo, maybe--

00:09:01.504 --> 00:09:03.670
I don't know-- if I were
going to be self-indulgent,

00:09:03.670 --> 00:09:05.378
it would be a lotus
flower because that's

00:09:05.378 --> 00:09:09.820
what my name means,
and maybe on my wrist.

00:09:09.820 --> 00:09:11.850
OK.

00:09:11.850 --> 00:09:14.142
And are you running for
president, yes or no?

00:09:14.142 --> 00:09:16.070
[LAUGHTER]

00:09:16.070 --> 00:09:16.990
Next question.

00:09:16.990 --> 00:09:18.270
All right.

